	dprr:hasNoteText "Fast. Cap. (names entire); Plin. NH 7.139, on Metellus; Chr. 354; Fast. Hyd.; Chr. Pasc.; Cassiod.; Zon. 8.16; see Degrassi 42f., 116, 436f. Metellus besieged Lilybaeum, and Fabius Drepanum; and both captured the island of Pelias (Zon. 8.16)." .
